{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/steam_sheeps.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br><br>Local lands conceal many secrets, wonders of nature, treasures, and artifacts. However, the main mystery remains the vast network of tunnels and caves that has existed at the bottom of the Lake for centuries. You are tasked with taking on the role of an explorer and delving into the depths of these ancient underground passages, as well as unraveling the secrets of the lake and its surroundings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open world and procedural generation</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/locs_shorter.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br>The world of \u201dRoam\u201d, due to procedural generation, random events and a hostile environment system creates unique situations with each playthrough. Danger lurks at every step: attacks from aggressive creatures, traps, and magical anomalies are just a small part of what you will face.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay variety</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/item_list.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br>You are given complete freedom to choose your path. Use diverse weapons and magic, prepare useful potions, find, create, and upgrade your equipment to navigate through the hostile environment. The choice of the exploration route is up to you. Players can choose to fight enemies or avoid battle, use cunning, agility, and magic instead of brute force. Overcome dangers alone or with friends, explore captivating locations, and discover new secrets.<br>Quests are designed to provide you with maximum freedom of action. Instead of leading you by the hand, they offer hints, allowing you to choose how to solve tasks and achieve goals. Your decisions influence the course of events and can open new opportunities or lead to unforeseen consequences.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>Explore, fight, survive!</i></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/steam_camp.gif?t=1737481067\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737481067","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/page.bg.jpg?t=1737481067","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737481067","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737481067","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/steam_sheeps.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br><br>Local lands conceal many secrets, wonders of nature, treasures, and artifacts. However, the main mystery remains the vast network of tunnels and caves that has existed at the bottom of the Lake for centuries. You are tasked with taking on the role of an explorer and delving into the depths of these ancient underground passages, as well as unraveling the secrets of the lake and its surroundings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open world and procedural generation</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662550/extras/locs_shorter.gif?t=1737481067\" /><br>The world of \u201d